headline: Mastercard Incorporated to Host Conference Call on Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2024 Financial Results
summary: PURCHASE, N.Y., January 09, 2025--On January 30, 2025, Mastercard (NYSE: MA) will host a conference call to discuss its fourth quarter and full year 2024 financial results.

headline: Mastercard Crypto Credential debuts in UAE and Kazakhstan
summary: The expansion will enable exchanges as well as Fuze to secure blockchain transactions for users in the region.
